1. See a commercial or ad about Pizza and get hungry.
2. Drive to The Garlic Knot in Westminster CO.
3. Say hi to Marko and tell him you want a classic Margherita Pie.
4. Wait 10-15 minutes for your pizza!

5. Take the pizza and leave the store.
6. Go to the gelato store and pick up a small bowl of pistachio gelato.
7. Drive home and enjoy!

8. Watch season 3 of The Bear on Hulu.
9. Fall asleep from food coma.